
The iPhone 12 is the latest and greatest in the iPhone line. It features an edge to edge OLED display with a resolution of 4K, a 12 megapixel camera, and a better battery. It is the same size as the iPhone 11 and has the same water and dust resistance. It can be purchased in three storage options: 64, 128, and 256gb. The iPhone 12 will cost $1,400 and will be released on December 3rd.
